Image.Alt: Seven scouts in class A uniforms performing a flag ceremony. Three scouts are holding the American flag at the center pole. The other four scouts are standing to the right and left of them at attention.
Four people, two of them are inside a ropped off area, two are standing outside. A sign says "Axe Yard" is hung on a tree just outside the roped off area.
Two adult leaders giving a selfie to the camera. One is holding up a mug, the other is giving a thumbs-up sign.
Six scouts sitting around a picnic table. A chess board is in the middle, and other scouts are playing cards.
Three scouts are sitting on a wooden log bench, and other is facing them in a chair, reading out of a book.
Seven scouts stand on a stage in front of people at night.
Group photo! 18 scouts are standing next to the troop trailer, which on on the right.
